text:
Nah, I'm thinking of a prank
to pull on Producer.

I-I see.
It'd help me out if you wouldn't, though.

Oh, right....
I recieved some baked sweets, want to eat some?

Oh, sure I'll have some...
There's quite the variety of flavors, huh.

There are. You can have whatever flavor you like.
I go and get some drinks.

Oh, and afterwards I'd like you
to try on your costume. Is that all right?
I'd prefer if you tell me that before I start eating...
